&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( english : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; bird ) is a 2010 hindi romantic drama directed by pradeep sarkar , produced by aditya chopra and starring neil nitin mukesh and deepika padukone in the lead roles . the film was released on 20 august 2010 under the yash raj films banner . the story of the film is partially inspired from the 1978 american film , ice castles and the 1999 tamil film , thulladha manamum thullum .